@zoltanman wrote:

Ok, find the l33thax method, and delete one of them. Also, find the fsBar method and delete one of them, and the animation method.

Now, for the startAnimation.

Declare this in player class.

public void startAnimation(int animIdx) { animationRequest = animIdx; animationWaitCycles = 0; }

Did you follow the whole tutorial? You didn’t add the variables for those EnemyHP, EnemyX, EnemyY, fsLockOn, and you don’t have the method poisonplayer.

public void PoisonPlayer() { Poisoned = false; PoisonClear = 0; PoisonDelay = 40; Poison = 1; Poison(); }
